            <lg xml:id="TK678">
<l>viṉaiyāl viṉaiyākkik kōṭa ṉaṉaikavuḷ </l>
<l>yāṉaiyāl yāṉaiyāt taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To make one undertaking the means of accomplishing another (similar to it) is like making one rutting elephant the means of capturing another</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
